                  <value>&quot;Boredom usually&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Boredom, anger and just being hungry in general.&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Boredom, anger, drunkeness&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;boredom, anger, happy&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Boredom, being in your period, and long bus rides for softball&quot;</value>
