                  <value>&quot;boredom, sadness, and if it has a good taste. &quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Boredom, sadness, anxiety&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;boredom, sadness, hungry&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Boredom, sadness, or with friends &quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Boredom!, sadness&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;I do not really eat \&quot;comfort food\&quot; but I guess sadness, special occasions, and anxiety &quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Loneliness / Homesick / Sadness&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;sadness&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Sadness and cravings&quot;</value>
