                  <value>&quot;Boredom, stress&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Boredom, stress, and it tastes good&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;boredom, stress, mood swings&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;boredom, stressed, sad&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Depression, comfort, accessibility &quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;I am always stressed out, and bored when I am in my apartment. &quot;</value>
